The Billings Bridge area is a large residential area of home owning age residents. This could come about maybe because of the need for cheap housing. The same case applies for the Big Rideau Lake community. Since there is an existent of waterfront homes, people flock down here for villas around the city. The small bay area residents have on older homes in the town.

There are available listings of such places to live in through an online dealer’s site who updates on newly acquired or sold homes each time as well as showing the kind of houses they have. A lot are available in the Country Roads category. The area lured residents, since there is scenery of the Ottawa River and boardwalk, boating, walking or cycling could be such that the topic is utopias. In this neighbourhood residents desire to meet each other, hence social activities are also celebrated.
